content: I've used the app for a couple of weeks. The app is very simple and easy to use. The best thing for me is the voice is very soothing an goes along without dominating the meditation. The main weakness for me is lacking time elapse display to show the length of time when for any reason I end or pause meditation. Also, there maybe some guided techniques that could be added to the voice especially for longer duration than 5 or 10 minutes.

It's simply a soothing voice helping to guide your mind through taking a moment to let go of everything else going on around you, and simply exist. Very refreshing.
